420
00:26:29,550 --> 00:26:31,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Lee So Won?</font>

421
00:26:32,089 --> 00:26:33,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa itu?</font>

422
00:26:33,730 --> 00:26:36,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, katakan padanya
kalau aku akan menemuinya.</font>

423
00:26:38,899 --> 00:26:41,069
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ada apa?
- Aku harus pergi.</font>

424
00:26:41,069 --> 00:26:43,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada rumor kalau seseorang
sedang diam-diam menyelidikiku.</font>

425
00:26:44,139 --> 00:26:45,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ingin bertemu denganku.</font>

426
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:47,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau gila? Apa yang akan kau lakukan
