441
00:28:07,520 --> 00:28:09,250
<font color=#FFFF00>"Le So Won, Orthopedi Amesou."</font>

442
00:28:09,250 --> 00:28:10,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee So Won-ssi?</font>

443
00:28:14,559 --> 00:28:18,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Kudengar kau menelepon ke Amerika
