446
00:28:24,169 --> 00:28:25,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Yeon Ju?</font>

447
00:28:26,540 --> 00:28:29,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Hubungan macam apa yang kalian
miliki untuk mengatakan itu?</font>

448
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:32,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku barus saja...</font>

449
00:28:33,609 --> 00:28:34,710
<font color=#FFFF00>...bercerai dengannya.</font>

450
00:28:39,180 --> 00:28:41,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitu, ya. Aku mengerti.</font>

451
00:28:43,159 --> 00:28:47,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Kudengar itu salahmu
sehingga kalian bercerai.</font>

452
00:28:48,230 --> 00:28:49,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu benar?</font>

453
00:28:49,329 --> 00:28:50,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu benar.</font>

454
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:52,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu benar salahku
sehingga kami bercerai.</font>

455
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:56,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika itu benar, kenapa
kau menyelidikiku?</font>

456
00:28:56,669 --> 00:28:59,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat kesal
setelah mendengarnya.</font>

457
00:29:00,339 --> 00:29:03,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau berusaha
memisahkan kami...</font>

458
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:04,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan niatku.</font>

459
00:29:05,409 --> 00:29:08,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku melakukannya
