486
00:30:53,119 --> 00:30:54,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia baik dan
lembut di dalam.</font>

487
00:30:56,859 --> 00:30:58,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong sayangi dia.</font>

488
00:30:59,930 --> 00:31:01,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuharap kau akan
