494
00:31:22,980 --> 00:31:24,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Permisi.</font>

495
00:31:58,149 --> 00:31:59,990
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau masih memiliki
perasaan untukku?</i></font>

496
00:32:00,290 --> 00:32:01,720
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau masih mencintaiku?</i></font>

497
00:32:05,419 --> 00:32:06,829
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kalau begitu,
