498
00:32:17,639 --> 00:32:19,099
<font color=#FFFF00>Yeon Ju.</font>

499
00:32:19,500 --> 00:32:20,569
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

500
00:32:20,809 --> 00:32:25,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah berbicara
