504
00:32:34,849 --> 00:32:37,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Benarkah? Syukurlah.</font>

505
00:32:37,690 --> 00:32:39,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Yeon Ju.</font>

506
00:32:39,730 --> 00:32:42,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tampak sedih?
