508
00:32:46,470 --> 00:32:49,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo, Yeon Ju.</font>

509
00:32:50,740 --> 00:32:55,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada banyak pembantu tua yang
belum pernah menikah seusiamu.</font>

510
00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:58,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi hidupmu berbalik dua kali.</font>

511
00:32:58,040 --> 00:32:59,409
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu juga kemampuanmu.</font>

512
00:32:59,409 --> 00:33:02,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Menikah dan memamerkannya.</font>

513
00:33:04,919 --> 00:33:07,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Bu, bukankah
menurutmu dia baik?</font>

514
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:12,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan melupakan So Won...</font>

515
00:33:12,859 --> 00:33:14,559
<font color=#FFFF00>...jika aku bersamanya, 'kan?</font>

516
00:33:15,059 --> 00:33:18,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja.</font>

517
00:33:18,629 --> 00:33:22,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tahu kenapa Ibu membeli rumah
